===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant-y|cop|y|}}

# To produce an object identical to a given object.
#: ''Please '''copy''' these reports for me''
# To imitate.
#: ''Don't '''copy''' my dance moves.''
#: ''Mom, he's '''copying''' me!''
# (''radio'') Receive a transmission successfully.
#: ''Do you '''copy'''?''

